title: Barrio Star
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Modern Mexican food. Uses local and organic ingredients. Casual atmosphere. Marks menu for veg, vegan, and gluten free. Vegan choices including tofu or soy chorizo tacos, a tamal, a bowl.
